All Classes

Class Description
FitnessFunction
This interface will be the lambda function for the fitness score of the genetic algorithm.
FitnessFunctions
This class will contain some standard fitness functions that may be used with a genetic algorithm.
GeneticAlgorithm
This class is the genetic algorithm base used for training a neural network structure.
GeneticAlgorithmUtil
This class will contain useful utility methods for the genetic algorithm class.
HiddenLayer
This class is the hidden layer for the Neural Network.
HighestOutputLayer
This class is the output layer for a neural network where the index of the highest value is returned.
InputLayer
This is a base input layer and simply outputs the input values received.
Layer<T>
This interface will be the individual computational layers for the Neural Network.
ListUtil
This class will hold utility functions for the List interface.
NeuralNetwork<O>
This class is the base NeuralNetwork.
Node
This class is the node generated for the layers within the neural network.
NodeGenerator
This class is intended used to generate a Node with a random weight.
NodeUtil
This class will contain utility methods for the Node class
OutputLayer<T,​O>
This interface will be the final layer or the output layer for the Neural Network.
RoundedOutputLayer
This class is the output layer for a Neural Network where it returns the output rounded to the nearest integer.
